eu.greenlightning.hypercubepdf

Enum HCPAreaBorder

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<HCPAreaBorder>
      • eu.greenlightning.hypercubepdf.HCPAreaBorder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<HCPAreaBorder>

    public enum HCPAreaBorder
extends Enum<HCPAreaBorder>
    Defines which of the four border parts of an HCPArea should be painted.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      BOTTOM_BORDER

      Paint all four border parts.

      NO_BORDER
      Do not paint any border parts.

      • combineWith

        public HCPAreaBorder combineWith(HCPAreaBorder other)
        Returns the HCPAreaBorder which is a combination between this border and the other border. That is the resulting border will paint all border parts painted by this border and all border parts painted by the other border. In other words, the resulting border will paint a given border part if this border or the other border (or both) paint it.
        Parameters:
        other - not null
        Returns:
        the combination of this border and the other border
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if other is null

      • combine

        public static HCPAreaBorder combine(HCPAreaBorder first,
                                    HCPAreaBorder second)
        Returns the HCPAreaBorder which is a combination between the two specified borders. That is the resulting border will paint all border parts painted by the first border and all border parts painted by the second border. In other words, the resulting border will paint a given border part if the first border or the second border (or both) paint it.
        Parameters:
        first - not null
        second - not null
        Returns:
        the combination of the first border and the second border
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if first or second is null
